    "description": "Follow Me is an independent platformer with adventure and puzzle elements. The little white rabbit's curiosity about what lies behind the door ends up taking him on a long and engaging adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256220/extras/33a2a1bb009622fe57741e502b24b8f5.poster.avif?t=1764668023\" width=620 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256220/extras/33a2a1bb009622fe57741e502b24b8f5.webm?t=1764668023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256220/extras/33a2a1bb009622fe57741e502b24b8f5.mp4?t=1764668023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The gameplay is based on the exploration of various lands and the interaction with the characters that you encounter, which may be friendly or hostile.<br>Our bunny, traveling through strange locations, helps the characters he meets, who also help in further adventure. He gains new skills and uncovers hidden secrets to reach the mysterious grand finale.<br>Beautiful graphics and gameplay refer to classic games from the era of 8-bit computers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256220/extras/57e7f82b484d4f5ac41695a721c89aaa.poster.avif?t=1764668023\" width=620 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256220/extras/57e7f82b484d4f5ac41695a721c89aaa.webm?t=1764668023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256220/extras/57e7f82b484d4f5ac41695a721c89aaa.mp4?t=1764668023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Follow the white rabbit.",
